  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I keep Instagram private from Facebook friends and contacts?",
  "response": "To keep your Instagram account private from Facebook friends and contacts, you can take the following steps:\n\n### 1. **Make Your Instagram Account Private**\n   - Go to your Instagram profile and tap the menu (three horizontal lines in the top-right corner).\n   - Tap **Settings** > **Privacy** > **Account Privacy**.\n   - Toggle on **Private Account**. This ensures only approved followers can see your posts and activity.\n\n### 2. **Unlink Your Instagram and Facebook Accounts**\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Accounts Center** (or **Linked Accounts** depending on your version).\n   - Find your Facebook account and tap it.\n   - Tap **Remove From Accounts Center** or **Unlink**.\n   - This will stop any sharing of activity between Instagram and Facebook.\n\n### 3. **Block Facebook Friends from Finding You**\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Privacy** > **Connections**.\n   - Turn off the option **Allow Facebook Friends to Follow You** or similar.\n   - This prevents Facebook friends from being suggested as followers on Instagram.\n\n### 4. **Manage Contacts Syncing**\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Privacy** > **Connections** > **Contact Syncing**.\n   - Turn off **Connect Contacts** to prevent Instagram from suggesting your account to contacts in your phone\u2019s address book.\n\n### 5. **Review and Remove Followers**\n   - Visit your followers list and remove anyone you don\u2019t want to have access to your account.\n   - Block specific users if necessary by going to their profile, tapping the three dots in the top-right corner, and selecting **Block**.\n\n### 6. **Avoid Sharing Activity to Facebook**\n   - If your accounts are still linked, avoid sharing Instagram posts, Stories, or activity to Facebook.\n   - When posting, ensure the Facebook sharing option is turned off.\n\n### 7. **Customize Your Blocked List**\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Privacy** > **Blocked Accounts**.\n   - Add specific Facebook friends or contacts you don\u2019t want to interact with on Instagram.\n\nBy following these steps, you can ensure your Instagram activity remains private from Facebook friends and contacts.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
